openai_api_key.description: An openAI API key to use. If left default, will use Steamship's API key.

model.description: Model to use for image generation. Must be one of: ['dall-e-2', 'dall-e-3']

n.description: Default number of images to generate for each prompt.

size.description: Default size of the output images. Must be one of:['1024x1024', '512x512', '256x256', '1792x1024', '1024x1792'].

max_retries.description: Maximum number of retries to make when generating.

request_timeout.description: Timeout for requests to OpenAI completion API. Default is 600 seconds.

quality.description: The quality of the image that will be generated. Must be one of: ['standard', 'hd'].'hd' creates images with finer details and greater consistency across the image. This param is only supported for `dall-e-3`.

style.description: The style of the generated images. Must be one of: ['vivid', 'natural']. Vivid causes the model to lean towards generating hyper-real and dramatic images. Natural causes the model to produce more natural, less hyper-real looking images. This param is only supported for `dall-e-3`.
